library(moments)
lipid <- read.csv("hf303-01-lipid-p.csv")
enzymeAct <- read.csv("hf303-06-enzyme-activity.csv")
names(lipid)[names(lipid) == "warming"] <- "treatment"
names(lipid)[names(lipid) == "soil.type"] <- "soil"
names(enzymeAct)[names(enzymeAct) == "warming"] <- "treatment"
enzymeAct$treatment[enzymeAct$treatment == "DC"] <- "C"
lipid <- lipid[,c("treatment","soil","plot","timepoint","doy","date","lipidp.dry")]
enzymeAct <- enzymeAct[,c("sample.id","treatment","soil","plot","timepoint","doy","date","enzyme","eea")]
vars <- qw(plot,treatment,soil,timepoint,sample.id,enzyme,eea,lipidp.dry,BG,CBH,BX,NAG,PO,HPO)
varIdxEnz <- which(names(enzymeAct) %in% vars)
varIdxLip <- which(names(lipid) %in% vars)
plotorder <- c(1,3,5,6,8,9,10,12,13,15,16,17)
enzymeSimp <- subset(enzymeAct, select = varIdxEnz, enzymeAct$timepoint=="T2" | enzymeAct$timepoint == "T6")
lipidSimp <- subset(lipid, select = varIdxLip, lipid$timepoint == "T2" | lipid$timepoint == "T6")
enzOrg <- pivot_wider(enzymeSimp, id_cols = c("soil","timepoint","treatment", "plot", "sample.id"), names_from = enzyme, values_from = eea)
enzOrg <- subset(enzOrg, select = c(qw(plot,treatment,soil,timepoint,BG,CBH,BX,NAG,PO,HPO)))
lipidT2Min <- subset(lipidSimp, select = c("plot","treatment","soil","timepoint","lipidp.dry"), lipidSimp$timepoint=="T2" & lipidSimp$soil == "Mineral")
lipidT6Min <- subset(lipidSimp, select = c("plot","treatment","soil","timepoint","lipidp.dry"), lipidSimp$timepoint=="T6" & lipidSimp$soil == "Mineral")
lipidT2Org <- subset(lipidSimp, select = c("plot","treatment","soil","timepoint","lipidp.dry"), lipidSimp$timepoint=="T2" & lipidSimp$soil == "Organic")
lipidT6Org <- subset(lipidSimp, select = c("plot","treatment","soil","timepoint","lipidp.dry"), lipidSimp$timepoint=="T6" & lipidSimp$soil == "Organic")
T2Min <- subset(enzOrg, select = c("plot","treatment","soil","timepoint","BG","CBH","BX","NAG","PO","HPO"), enzOrg$timepoint=="T2" & enzOrg$soil == "Mineral")
T2Org <- subset(enzOrg, select = c("plot","treatment","soil","timepoint","BG","CBH","BX","NAG","PO","HPO"), enzOrg$timepoint=="T2" & enzOrg$soil == "Organic")
T6Min <- subset(enzOrg, select = c("plot","treatment","soil","timepoint","BG","CBH","BX","NAG","PO","HPO"), enzOrg$timepoint=="T6" & enzOrg$soil == "Mineral")
T6Org <- subset(enzOrg, select = c("plot","treatment","soil","timepoint","BG","CBH","BX","NAG","PO","HPO"), enzOrg$timepoint=="T6" & enzOrg$soil == "Organic")
lipidT2Min <- lipidT2Min[match(plotorder, lipidT2Min$plot),]
lipidT2Org <- lipidT2Org[match(plotorder, lipidT2Org$plot),]
lipidT6Min <- lipidT6Min[match(plotorder, lipidT6Min$plot),]
lipidT6Org <- lipidT6Org[match(plotorder, lipidT6Org$plot),]
T2Min$lipidp.dry <- cbind(lipidT2Min$lipidp.dry)
T2Org$lipidp.dry <- cbind(lipidT2Org$lipidp.dry)
T6Min$lipidp.dry <- cbind(lipidT6Min$lipidp.dry)
T6Org$lipidp.dry <- cbind(lipidT6Org$lipidp.dry)
organizedchart <- rbind(T2Min,T2Org)
organizedchart <- rbind(organizedchart,T6Min)
organizedchart <- rbind(organizedchart,T6Org)
organizedchartSoil <-melt(organizedchart[,c(3,5:11)], id.vars="soil")
## Warning: attributes are not identical across measure variables; they will be
## dropped
organizedchartTreat <-melt(organizedchart[,c(2,5:11)], id.vars="treatment")
## Warning: attributes are not identical across measure variables; they will be
## dropped
organizedchartTime <-melt(organizedchart[,c(4,5:11)], id.vars="timepoint")
## Warning: attributes are not identical across measure variables; they will be
## dropped
ggplot(aes(x=soil, y=value),data=organizedchartSoil)+geom_boxplot(size=2)+
  facet_grid(~variable) +
  theme_bw(base_size=15)+
  xlab("Horizon") +
  ylab("Standard mean")

ggplot(aes(x=treatment, y=value),data=organizedchartTreat)+geom_boxplot(size=2)+

organizedchart$BX.log <- log10(organizedchart$BX)
organizedchart$NAG.log <- log10(organizedchart$NAG)
